{"type": "article", "id": 24789, "title": "有个工厂仓库改的住宅，理想化得不可思议", "description": "可以在院子里看看天、晒晒太阳。", "date": "2016-03-31T15:55:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 143, "name": "设计"}, {"id": 18, "name": "建筑"}, {"id": 11871, "name": "住宅"}, {"id": 8019, "name": "改造"}, {"id": 25675, "name": "院子"}, {"id": 25676, "name": "室内庭院"}, {"id": 21048, "name": "仓库"}, {"id": 22674, "name": "工业"}, {"id": 25677, "name": "Architects EAT"}], "category": 17, "author": 451727, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 374, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115457W1DsBZySdA4R5kQ7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">一个位于澳大利亚墨尔本郊区的砖材质的工业仓库，被改建成一个复式的住宅。<br></p>\n<p>这栋建筑有 125 年的历史，250 平方米的面积，原本是一家巧克力工厂的仓库。</p>\n<p>改建后的最大的特点是空出一块可以看到屋顶的全层高的内部庭院，阳光和天空的景观透过屋顶进入室内，室内庭院扮演了保持室内室外交流的”肺“的角色。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021154522xLDjIOhY6eVfmQb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66363636\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115453BtCKqriP9SUeFRj0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33096927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">建筑原本的混合砖墙被裸露在外，钢铁框架构成了独特的功能分区。可伸缩折叠的玻璃窗户可以向露台和室内庭院开放，展开可以形成空间分隔，而折叠起来又可以让室内室外保持连续。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115453fzhwC8vgjpE5YFaA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115453XyaKlQZhP3F9uoA2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66627219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115454EGIx5DlQ67r4bsUm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>如卧室、书房等私密功能的空间被安排在了一楼，并通过一座桥和厨房和起居室连接。搭配现代风格的木质的家具，形成一个开放灵活的室内空间。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115455plGO7s6LVA5HUu4m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75050505\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115455yn3f2rJwq47gbCaN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75166889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115456VIRpBlFW0MZyDCLr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74867021\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115456PmXQcAy5TVbwL1hv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33096927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>这项建筑改造由澳大利亚建筑室内设计公司 Architects EAT在 2015 年完成，在今年 3 月 24 日获得本届澳大利亚室内设计住宅类<a href=\"http://gallery.australianinteriordesignawards.com/year:2016/awardid:154/entryid:2030\">大奖</a>。</p>\n<p class=\"\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p>\n<p>题图和文内图来自 <a href=\"http://gallery.australianinteriordesignawards.com/year:2016/awardid:154/entryid:2030\">australianinteriordesignawards</a>、<a href=\"http://eatas.com.au/projects/detail/fitzroy-loft\">eatas</a></p>\n\n"}